citation: Proclamation under the Health Service Establishments Act 2006 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Health Service Establishments Act 2006

I, the Lieutenant-Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Health Service Establishments Act 2006 fix 1 October 2011 as the day on which that Act commences.

19 September 2011

E. C. CRAWFORD

Lieutenant-Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

MICHELLE O'BYRNE

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 28 September 2011

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
